title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's playoff action with Jeff Van Gundy. Are the Celtics too much for the Heat to handle given their injuries? Reds 1st Baseman Joey Votto joins us for another entertaining interview and shares his thoughts on being a potential Hall of Famer.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
